It is a code editor written in java.
Language used : JAVA
tools used : netbeans.

It can display output , take input at runtime and display compile error.
It provides syntax highlighting,auto-completion, find and replace, undo/redo, font size and style and keyboard shortcuts. 
It shows line number and column number at the bottom of editor.
It also display a menu on right click with features copy, paste, find and run.
It display compilation time on status bar.It can show recently opened files and has features of resizing various panes.
These fundamentals are implemented by using Abstract Window Toolkit(AWT)  that supports the control like textarea, textfield,  checkbox, pushbutton, labels etc.
